â†’ Causal Consistency:
1ï¸âƒ£  Preserves the causality between related events.ğŸ”„
2ï¸âƒ£  Ensures all nodes agree on the ordering of events.ğŸ”—
3ï¸âƒ£  Important for maintaining application semantics and correctness.ğŸ§©
