â†’ Monotonic Reads and Writes:
1ï¸âƒ£  Guarantees clients observe monotonically increasing sequences of values or updates.ğŸ“ˆ
2ï¸âƒ£  Ensures clients always see the most recent data and writes are applied in the same order.ğŸ”„
